{"tid":692943,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國肯德基將推素食炸雞　保證不改秘方","createTime":"2018-06-07T05:22:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T06:16:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a5c7ca2e6c09bd170f52930c8187a68bd0a1eef0","tid":692943,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:22:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180607/s00005/1528345071133\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180607%2Fs00005%2F1528345071133&d=R949l7d43WBU2XNm%2FySWvZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=6f641279\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180607%2Fs00005%2F1528345071133&h=3c82de70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180607/s00005/1528345071133</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180607/s00005/7609aaef9272f90d7014bd1025758ce3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180607%2Fs00005%2F7609aaef9272f90d7014bd1025758ce3.jpg&h=6c2c4d0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n市人愈來愈追求健康飲食，餐飲業都開拓素食市場，英國大型連鎖快餐店肯德基亦準備分一杯羹，研發素食炸雞，期望2019年在英國全面推出。<br />\n<br />\n素食炸雞是英國肯德基健康餐單計劃之一，希望將每份餐單的卡路里降低20%，並擬2020年後推出各種低於600卡路里的套餐。<br />\n<br />\n英國肯德基表示：「一旦我們完善了配方，我們打算今年與客戶進行測試，如果一切順利，希望在2019年推出新的素食選擇。」<br />\n<br />\n英國肯德基又表示，新餐單如同原有餐單一樣美味，「這一個棘手的挑戰，因為我們的支持者絕對喜歡我們的傳統食譜，我們不會改變『上校』的11種草藥和香料的秘密配方。」"},{"pid":"405034df5954bf9555e6948cda5000c98b290b42","tid":692943,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"223683a56c805b9dc97c29a0d3df470aee8ac675","tid":692943,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:24:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74bb7efd50ec1dce918925623d85c4d790411418","tid":692943,"uid":34213,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"執錯雞就仆街了"},{"pid":"ac74717d527a8d1b2ccd740563a2dfd317d77d51","tid":692943,"uid":21423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:25:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c81b05c729af4687ed14def59e74654f18786482","tid":692943,"uid":58140,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:26:53.000Z","msg":"又想食雞又想食素<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f1aa635f9b049895844a232adba315d232f19b","tid":692943,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:27:24.000Z","msg":"啲雞已經難食<br />\n重要素炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dfdb9cab513d69e788ed5690042d0c6070b90dd","tid":692943,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:29:10.000Z","msg":"因為有素食撚投訴無素食？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78ad7fb964bf474efb79559d841144189e7e855f","tid":692943,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:29:42.000Z","msg":"香港幾時有素食ptgf玩？"},{"pid":"170d6520aa39203a2afc1d7c2225e4d3db116111","tid":692943,"uid":21052,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66f1aa635f9b049895844a232adba315d232f19b","tid":692943,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:27:24.000Z","msg":"啲雞已經難食<br />\n重要素炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:53:52.000Z","msg":"英國KFC好好食喎"},{"pid":"d1ed78775e0ae019ef1ce626ab6c3741da540d90","tid":692943,"uid":51114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T05:55:39.000Z","msg":